{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Escape the room using your chemistry knowledge! Explore the clues lying around. Clear up the poisonous gas blocking your exit. Turn a toxic combustion reaction into a regular combustion reaction. Heat up different liquids to obtain the needed molecules.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Curriculum fit:</strong> Oxygen and combustion are taught in the curriculum of 8th grade Basic Chemistry in most countries. However, the VR lesson can be enjoyed by players of any age wishing to learn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Download the free Lesson Plan under \u2018View the Manual\u2019 on the right to maximize learning from this VR lesson, including a short quiz.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Playing this VR lesson is easier after student has completed Reaction Balancing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FIGURE OUT HOW TO ESCAPE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Move around the room and explore the posters and whiteboards left behind for clues on how to escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494430/extras/O2_1.gif?t=1734862724\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">USE A BUNSEN BURNER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Heat up different liquids using a Bunsen burner. Each liquid produces molecules which could - or could not - be useful at the balancing table.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494430/extras/O2_2.gif?t=1734862724\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SOLVE THE COMBUSTION PUZZLE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Solve the challenge of turning a balanced toxic combustion reaction into a balanced non-toxic combustion reaction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494430/extras/O2_3.gif?t=1734862724\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CELEBRATE BY EXPLORING</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After you have cleared your path for exit, reward yourself by exploring a bit more before escaping the room.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494430/extras/O2_4.gif?t=1734862724\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When you finish the game, take the test at the back of the Lesson Plan to see if you can balance equations on paper as well as you can in this VR lesson.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494430/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734862724","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494430/page.bg.jpg?t=1734862724","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494430/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734862724","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494430/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734862724","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Downloadable Content","id":21}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Escape the room using your chemistry knowledge! Explore the clues lying around. Clear up the poisonous gas blocking your exit. Turn a toxic combustion reaction into a regular combustion reaction. Heat up different liquids to obtain the needed molecules.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Curriculum fit:</strong> Oxygen and combustion are taught in the curriculum of 8th grade Basic Chemistry in most countries. However, the VR lesson can be enjoyed by playe